---
import aboutImage from '../assets/About-Image_Tiny.webp';
---

<section id="about" class="section about">
	<div class="container">
		<h2 class="section-title">About the Race</h2>
		<div class="about-content">
			<div class="about-text">
				<div class="card">
					<h3 class="card-title">The Ultimate Trail Experience</h3>
					<p class="card-text">
						The Tsitsikamma Ultra is a challenging 50km trail run that takes you through some of South Africa's most spectacular indigenous forests, coastal paths, and mountain trails. This is not just a race, it's an adventure that will test your limits while showcasing the breathtaking beauty of the Garden Route.
					</p>
					<p class="card-text">
						Starting at Storms River Petroport, the route winds through ancient forests, crosses streams, and offers stunning mountain vistas before finishing at Covie. With a total elevation gain of 2,500m, this ultra demands respect, preparation, and determination.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="about-image-container">
				<div class="card image-card">
					<img src={aboutImage.src} alt="Trail runner going up the hill at Bloukrans section of the Tsitsikamma Ultra" class="about-image" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.about {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--background-color) 0%, rgba(34, 51, 59, 0.8) 100%);
		scroll-margin-top: 60px;
	}

	.about-content {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
		align-items: stretch;
	}

	.about-text {
		display: flex;
	}

	.about-image-container {
		display: flex;
	}

	.about-text .card,
	.about-image-container .card {
		height: 100%;
		flex: 1;
	}

	.card-title {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--primary-color);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.card-text {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.card-text:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.image-card {
		padding: 0;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.about-image {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}

	.about-image:hover {
		transform: scale(1.05);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.about-content {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}
	}
</style>